/blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae36babc1c58bdd053dc7683669b9f98819ded74","tid":425222,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"以前未試過，但近呢兩個月開始有呢種感覺<br />\n好想可以去返以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f8c2d39fe88f19f802dcb11200ecdd60fda23b","tid":425222,"uid":20789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"留名 覺得自己愈黎愈獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bab2478e5c17f85e679200e02acc26c0c56fdb9","tid":425222,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"每日set個小目標比自已 好快就可以開始慢慢改善架啦<br />\n例如今日最底限度要點點點咁 <br />\n可能係放假果陣執好間房呀<br />\n放工最底限度要打返陣機咁<br />\n<br />\n其實搵返個目標 你為左達成佢 你就會發現好多野要做架啦<br />\n<br />\n我反而多野想做到唔做邊樣先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住又浪費左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80185e92cacb512db68f9223ff341331ae9054e8","tid":425222,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"有冇打飛機習慣?頻率?"},{"pid":"bf80b3dcedb199331a0a38914ee8dbca5984092d","tid":425222,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b93aab0ed061f2cd29ab06c7a20103de54ef9c4","tid":425222,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d005a0e22549cabf29157a167cc4fb701aa49a","tid":425222,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c3d832d4cae61015c91dfa5aed33e0917d0737","tid":425222,"uid":70760,"like"