女都唔驚悶親人啦係咪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾年前考左日文N2<br />\n曾經諗過重溫加自修N1<br />\n但完全冇動力, 諗起要溫書, 不了"},{"pid":"d2b4d760fa963719358385c312b5713a58f01509","tid":425222,"uid":28741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"每日返工放工"},{"pid":"ce02d003fafeae92ca2403b2eb45c5618b9eafb2","tid":425222,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b987b0c10f6dd26ae91fae7a152f225cb0c73308","tid":425222,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有乜解決方法"},{"pid":"bd4aa13e8377d6044b789f0727411a7066a2f97c","tid":425222,"uid":5463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"情況差唔多<br />\n但會同自己講做唔做都冇所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  過到自己就得啦<br />\n有新野玩？咁又點 新野不停咁出 玩得幾多 有得玩咪玩囉<br />\n去試新餐廳？一路都食開果幾間 幾好食丫 洗乜特登去咁遠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0feefcc0dfe970d1028559106968046c99bf42","tid":425222,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對任何野失去興趣可以係抑鬱先兆<br />\n注意心理健康呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做下運動養成習慣真係會有幫助</blockquote><br />\n咁我應該抑鬱左好耐"},{"pid":"dc9b0544c394444e75ca3acba3ea38bb9990381f","tid":425222,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T18:22:45.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經進化到冇乜感覺"},{"p